            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9900,
            "LocalizeKR": "목욕 후의\n후르츠 밀크……\n이것은 정말 훌륭하군!",
            "LocalizeJP": "お風呂上がりの\nフルーツ牛乳……\nこれは素晴らしいな！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20009,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2000901,
            "DisplayOrder": 520,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4300,
            "LocalizeKR": "응?\n무슨 일 있는가,\n콤라드?",
            "LocalizeJP": "うん？\nどうかしたのか、\nカムラッド？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20009,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2000901,
            "DisplayOrder": 530,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8650,
            "LocalizeKR": "이 몸의 얼굴에\n뭔가 묻은 건가?",
            "LocalizeJP": "おいらの顔に\n何かついてるか？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20009,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2000901,
            "DisplayOrder": 540,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11570,
            "LocalizeKR": "……뭐?\n입 주변에 수염같은\n자국이……!?",
            "LocalizeJP": "……なに？\n口の周りに\n髭みたいな痕が……！？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20009,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2000901,
            "DisplayOrder": 550,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8150,
            "LocalizeKR": "우와, 정말이잖아?\n우유만 마셨을 뿐인데,\n이렇게 멋진 수염이……!",
            "LocalizeJP": "うおぉ、本当だ！？\n牛乳を飲んだだけなのに、\nこんなに素晴らしい髭が！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20009,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2000901,
            "DisplayOrder": 560,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10870,
            "LocalizeKR": "맛있는 음료를\n마셨을 뿐인데,\n새로운 수염까지\n얻을 수 있다니……",
            "LocalizeJP": "こんなに美味しい\n飲み物なのに、\n新しい髭まで手に入るとは……",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20009,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2000901,
            "DisplayOrder": 570,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13220,
            "LocalizeKR": "굉장하군!\n콤라드, 좀 더 가져오게!\n좀 더 이 후르츠 밀크를\n잔뜩 가져오는 거야!",
            "LocalizeJP": "素晴らしい！\nカムラッド、もっとだ！\nもっとこのフルーツ牛乳を\nたくさん取ってきてくれ！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
